1.Decide on a business to order your pizza from.
    a. Must be 4 stars or higher.
        1.https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=pizza&find_loc=Birmingham%2C%20AL&ns=1&cflt=pizza&sortby=rating
    b. How much are you willing to spend?
        1. Cheap : https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=pizza&find_loc=Birmingham%2C%20AL&ns=1&ed_attrs=RestaurantsPriceRange2.4&attrs=RestaurantsPriceRange2.1 
        2. Expensive : https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=pizza&find_loc=Birmingham%2C%20AL&ns=1&ed_attrs=RestaurantsPriceRange2.1%2CRestaurantsPriceRange2.2%2CRestaurantsPriceRange2.4&attrs=RestaurantsPriceRange2.3
2.Go through the menu.
    a. Check for deals on the menu.
3.Choose the pizza that you want.
    a. Look for suggestions & images from reviewers.
4.Place the order.
    a. Choose order method (Online or Phone).
5.Make a payement.
    a. Select card that recieves the most points.
    